<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">of both sides with x2, we must put a + in front of the number.</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">Two Solutions with Absolute Value</p>

