<h3 style="margin-top: 5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">298. Kiki’s teacher wrote the following riddle on</h3>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">@ 14. If (x, y) is the solution to the system of</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">the board: “There are two integers I am</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">equations below, what is the value of y?</p>

