<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">On the ACT, you often need to <strong style="color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;">factor</strong> quadratics. Factoring can help you simplify expressions or identify the</p>

