<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">As you can see in this example, we only need to use the identity to solve. When you see a sin?6 or cos*6 term</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">in a question, do not think of SOH-CAH-TOA. Instead, find how you can use the identity to solve as we did in</p>

