<h3 style="margin-top: 5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">333. To solve, we start by setting up the Law of Sines equation.</h3>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">We want to solve for k, so first we need to multiply both sides by 92.</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">Ok, now for the fun (hard) part! We know what sin(k°) is equal to, so to solve for k we need to use the</p>

