<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">To determine if the correct answer is C or D, we need to find the period. Looking at the graph, we see that the</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">period is 477. Remember, the easiest way to find the period from a graph is to look for the distance between</p>

