<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">We know there are 80 total marbles, so we can set up an equation to solve for the unknown number of red</p>

<ul style="margin: 0.3rem 0 0.5rem 0; padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.5;">
  <li style="margin: 0.15rem 0;">10</li>
</ul>

<h3 style="margin-top: 5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;">6. The answer is C.</h3>

