<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">Radians are another unit to measure angles. Just like we can measure temperature in Fahrenheit or Celsius, we</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">can measure an angle in degrees or radians. For the ACT, you need memorize the conversion below:</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">To convert between radians and degrees, use following 2 rules:</p>

