<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">Sometimes questions with <strong style="color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;">parallel lines</strong> will not always look like the <strong style="color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;">parallel lines</strong> in the figure. Ifthe lines</p>

