<h4 style="margin: 0 0 1rem 0; padding-left: 0.75rem; border-left: 4px solid #b91c1c; color: #000000; font-weight: 700;">Example 2: In the standard (x, y) coordinate plane, a line passes through points (9,7) and (—1,3) and</h4>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">has a <strong style="color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;">slope</strong> of 3. What is the value of r?</p>

