<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">where m is the <strong style="color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;">slope</strong> and b is the <strong style="color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;">y-intercept</strong>.</p>

