<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">Use the following information to answer questions</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">Dale’s Donuts sells donut boxes in two sizes: a</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">6-donut box for $5.25 and a 12-donut box for</p>

