<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">There are other ways to factor quadratics. If you have a different method that works for you, use that method.</p>

<p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0;">We will not review factoring any more beyond this example in this book. If you need to review factoring, look</p>

